A dynamic, painterly illustration of a fiery, crimson-skinned humanoid warrior, radiating intense rage, wielding a goblet overflowing with bubbling, glowing red liquid, attacking a shadowy, disoriented figure. The background is a swirling vortex of smoke and embers, reflecting the chaotic energy of the effect. Dramatic lighting, m15-conspiracy style, detailed textures, vibrant colors, action-oriented composition.